main event: An unidentified object was observed for five minutes, blinking red and green, and had propeller-like appendages.
interesting points: The object was reported to be slightly larger than an automobile.,The object had no discernible formation.,Witness observed the object traveling from northwest to southeast and then turning south and north.,The object was directly overhead during the observation.,There was no sound associated with the object.
sighted object: an oblong object with blinking red and green lights
